name: valentina cy - i like your heart

metadata.description:
A few months ago I fell head over heels for a guy who was in denial that I liked him at all. We went on a trip together, we went on dates, and he still didn't think I had real feelings for him. I was so annoyed so I finally wrote this song and sent it to him. He still tells me to this day that he doesn't believe me. Even after I wrote an entire album about the guy. 

I wrote, produced, and mixed this from my parents house. 

I hope it makes you feel like you're falling in love.
metadata.name: i like your heart  #1
metadata.title: i like your heart
